<topic template="Default" modified="2026-06-15T10:58:42.457Z" lasteditedby="tim" version="2" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../helpproject.xsd">
  <title>show memory</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>1024 MB</keyword>
    <keyword>--mem</keyword>
    <keyword>memory array</keyword>
    <keyword>memorySize</keyword>
    <keyword>show memory</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">SRM - show memory</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">The memory array is reported in the configuration table:</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">Array # Size Base Addr</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"> 0 1024 MB 000000000</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">Total Good Memory = 1024 MBytes, Total Bad Pages = 0</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">The default system memory is 1024 MB (set by <text styleclass="Code Example">[System] memorySize</text> in the ini); the size can be overridden at launch with <text styleclass="Code Example">--mem</text>.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="SeeAlso">See Also.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="show-config">show config</link></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="--Configuring----------(moved-">Configuring</link></para>
  </body>
</topic>
